name=Player Model Reload Utility
id=PlayerModelReloadUtil
description=Recovers from the B42 invisible-character bug without reloading your save. Most often it's the wall-cutaway hide system leaving you invisible-but-functional after passing behind a basement stairwell wall (your render alpha gets stuck at 0). This forces your character's alpha back to fully visible (plus a model-data rebuild) so you reappear in place. Trigger via a rebindable keybind (default INSERT) or right-click in-game > Utilities > Reload Player Model. Only changes rendering, never the world/grid, so it can't affect your position. Standalone, no dependencies, load order irrelevant. Safe to remove.
modversion=1.1.0
